ass="shell grid2"><div class="image"><img src="assets/images/mako-pack.jpg" alt="MAKO ingredients"></div><div><span class="eyebrow">Ingredient architecture</span><h2 class="display">Four layers of purpose.</h2><div class="timeline"><div><strong>Marine</strong><p>Fish and seafood create the defining foundation.</p></div><div><strong>Energy</strong><p>Selected grains and roots support the daily profile.</p></div><div><strong>Functional</strong><p>Seeds and oils are chosen for specific roles.</p></div><div><strong>Restraint</strong><p>No artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section soft"><div class="shell"><div class="cta"><div><h2>Shared ingredient world. Different nutritional responsibility.</h2><p>Dogs and cats require their own validated suitability and guidance.</p></div><a class="button light" href="nutrition.html">Nutrition approach</a></div></div></section>'''
page('ingredients.html','Ingredients | MAKO','Explore the MAKO fish-first ingredient philosophy.',ing)

nut=hero('Species-aware nutrition','One MAKO world.<br>Two nutritional pathways.','Dogs and cats can share a brand while receiving product development built around their own needs.')+'''<section class="section"><div class="shell species"><article><i>D</i><h3>For dogs</h3><p>Canine products are developed around life stage, body condition, activity and measured daily feeding.</p><div class="timeline"><div><strong>Protein</strong><p>Fish-led foundation.</p></div><div><strong>Energy</strong><p>Matched to activity and condition.</p></div><div><strong>Routine</strong><p>Consistent measured meals.</p></div></div></article><article><i>C</i><h3>For cats</h3><p>Feline products require their own nutrient validation, serving guidance and hydration awareness.</p><div class="timeline"><div><strong>Species</strong><p>Dedicated suitability validation.</p></div><div><strong>Meals</strong><p>Measured portions across the day.</p></div><div><strong>Health</strong><p>Professional support for specific needs.</p></div></div></article></div></section><section class="section darkSection"><div class="shell grid4"><article class="card"><h3>Marine foundation</h3><p>A clear reason to choose MAKO.</p></article><article class="card"><h3>Daily vitality</h3><p>Consistent nourishment and wellbeing.</p></article><article class="card"><h3>Validation</h3><p>Claims follow the exact formula.</p></article><article class="card"><h3>Trust</h3><p>Clear language without exaggeration.</p></article></div></section>'''
